cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.CY

This paper deals with privacy and security issues related to geo-tagged data in a marketplace setting. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques to enable searching and filtering of data based on geo-tags. The use of blockchain technology suggests a possible connection to distributed systems (cs.DS) as well. Finally, the paper deals with spam-resilience mechanisms, which could be related to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
